<div class="ugc-mod reading-notes">
  <div class="hd">
    <h2>
      读书笔记&nbsp;&nbsp;· · · · · ·&nbsp;
          <span class="pl">(<a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/2375972/annotation">共<span property="v:count">43</span>篇</a>)</span>

    </h2>

      <a class="redbutt rr j a_show_login" href="https://www.douban.com/register?reason=annotate" rel="nofollow"><span>我来写笔记</span></a>
  </div>
  

    <div class="bd">
      <ul class="inline-tabs">
        <li class="on"><a href="#rank" id="by_rank" >按有用程度</a></li>
        <li><a href="#page" id="by_page" >按页码先后</a></li>
        <li><a href="#time" id="by_time" >最新笔记</a></li>
      </ul>
      
  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="19333280">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/caoyi555/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1939857-110.jpg" alt="星条旗永不落" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19333280/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/19333280/" class="">第5页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/caoyi555/" class=" " title="星条旗永不落">星条旗永不落</a>
                (無逸。)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="19333280">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">今朝风日好，或恐有人来

董桥曾引吴湖帆句“无客尽日静，有风终夜凉”，两诗相形，境界高下可见，前者殷勤得堕于肉麻。至李拔可有句“叩门必吾党，争忍径不扫”，则益见狭隘矣。读丰子恺《护生画集》，每有矫情做作之感，即农妇剖鳞，置几草间，垂钓江渚之流，亦一概呵斥以侩子手，缘缘堂主人之玻璃心，殆非今世圣母们可以望及。又，董桥以为此诗系出吴湖帆，其实吴乃照录黄庭坚《谪居黔南十首》，而鲁直又全袭自白居易《竹窗》...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-06-30 20:46</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">5人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>今朝风日好，或恐有人来</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>董桥曾引吴湖帆句“无客尽日静，有风终夜凉”，两诗相形，境界高下可见，前者殷勤得堕于肉麻。至李拔可有句“叩门必吾党，争忍径不扫”，则益见狭隘矣。读丰子恺《护生画集》，每有矫情做作之感，即农妇剖鳞，置几草间，垂钓江渚之流，亦一概呵斥以侩子手，缘缘堂主人之玻璃心，殆非今世圣母们可以望及。又，董桥以为此诗系出吴湖帆，其实吴乃照录黄庭坚《谪居黔南十首》，而鲁直又全袭自白居易《竹窗》诗，见钱锺书《宋诗选注》。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

